{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0a93712075","title":"关于注意报道提拔新生力量的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fd08a0810a","index":0,"year":1964,"month":7,"day":4,"articleId":"0a93712075","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"干部和干部政策","id":"3df4ae75e1","type":"主题"},{"name":"彭真","id":"5fd56865b0","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"83c3a570df","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吴冷西，当时任新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑。"},{"id":"80650c50c6","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"安子文，当时任中共中央组织部部长。定一，即陆定一，当时任中共中央书记处书记、中央宣传部部长。瑞卿，即罗瑞卿，当时任中共中央书记处书记、中国人民解放军总参课长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"55c38f78df","type":"title","text":"关于注意报道提拔新生力量的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83c3a570df","type":"paragraph","text":"吴冷西响同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80650c50c6","type":"paragraph","text":"怀柔县一渡河支部提拔新生力量的做法，各省可能都有，要广泛采访、转载，在几年之内做到每县，每社，每个工厂、学校、机关都有报道，但要是真实的，典型的。固步自封的反面材料，也要登一点。这个问题，报社和通讯社应当讨论一下。并与各省、市、区联系，要他们也一样做。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e053c27bf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc6ed16ad3","type":"paragraph","text":"七月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a95a4ff065","type":"paragraph","text":"此件并送彭真、安子文、定一、瑞卿四同志阅","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8eba3a9e0","type":"paragraph","text":"[I指1964年7月4日《人民日报》第二版关于北京市怀柔县一渡河党支部提拔新生力量的报道。报道说，几年来，该支部先后提拨了30岁以下的干部17名，分别担任了党支部副书记、副大队长、大队会计、团支部书记等职务。老干部随时随地注意对他们进行教育、严格要求，帮助他们不断提高。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":469,"end":469}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4befe36760","type":"title","text":"关于注意报道提拔新生力量的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4cd999edd","type":"paragraph","text":"吴冷西同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ecec507b08","type":"paragraph","text":"怀柔县一渡河支部提拔新生力量的做法，各省可能都有，要广泛采访、转载，在几年之内做到每县，每社，每个工厂、学校、机关都有报道，但要是真实的，典型的。固步自封的反面材料，也要登一点。这个问题，报社和通讯社应当讨论一下。并与各省、市、区联系，要他们也一样做。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0a93712075","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}